#

Creamy Mushroom and Spinach Pasta

25 min
$12
650 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Protein

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

PastaQuick MealComfort Food

Description

A hearty and creamy pasta dish with sautéed mushrooms and fresh spinach, perfect for a quick yet satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • pasta (fettuccine or penne): 8 oz
  • fresh spinach: 4 cups
  • mushrooms (sliced): 2 cups
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • parmesan cheese (grated): 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
